Interface ExternalDataRequest

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<Property>

    public interface ExternalDataRequest
extends Iterable<Property>
    The class describes the request that is made to the service. The Iterable interface can by used to walk through all the property objects.

    Ricardo Belfor

      • getExternalDataIdentifier

        String getExternalDataIdentifier()
        A string that indicates the state of the data that was returned by the external data service. The request must include this identifier if the requestMode parameter is set to one of these values:
        • inProgressChanges
        • finalNewObject
        • finalExistingObject
        This API makes sure it has a default value.
